Description: Lightning-fast Passive Subdomain Discovery Tool
 subcat is a high-performance passive subdomain enumeration tool
 designed for security professionals and bug bounty hunters.
 Provides rapid discovery and categorization of subdomains using
 multiple data sources and intelligence gathering techniques.
